snippet.title: World of Warcraft: Battle for Azeroth Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description: Tensions between the Alliance and Horde have erupted, and a new age of war has begun. For more info on the game, or to opt in to the beta, head to http://worldofwarcraft.com
